last_episode_to_air.overview: The Barbapapa are back on DVD! Through their new adventures, the Barbapapa and his family transmit to children, with poetry and humor, current messages, positive values ...

seasons.name: Saison 1
seasons.overview: Barbapapa was born one day in the kindergarten Claudine and François. "Hup, hup, hup, Barbatruc": he discovers that he can transform into all kinds of things! He then meets Barbamama and falls in love. The family then grew into seven magnificent barbab babies: Barbibul, Barbotine, Barbouille, Barbalala, Barbidou, Barbabelle and Barbidur. The start of a great series of family adventures! ...
